Package: open-agenda
Architecture: all
Version: 1.0.0
Maintainer: Open-Agenda Team <team@open-agenda.org>
Depends: python3, python3-tk
Description: Open-Agenda - Smart Local Calendar & Task Manager
 The best agenda in the world - Open Source, intelligent and easy to use!
 .
 Features:
  - Beautiful modern dark interface
  - Interactive monthly calendar
  - Add, edit and delete events
  - Save and load data from JSON files
  - Local storage - your data stays on your device
  - Fully open source and free!
